modName: Araniel - Dunmer-like Racemenu Preset for Imperial Females
summary: As the title says, this is a preset mimicking the appearance of Dunmer females on an Imperial female character.
descriptionHtml:
This preset was made with a female imperial in mind. It was born out of the need to represent how this character was supposed to be a half-dunmer, half-imperial of sorts...although I'm not exactly sure which side ended up being predominant through out the whole process.

With the main file I've also Included optional files that comprehend other older (maybe in the future, newer) versions for Araniel. Thus I have available:
[list]
[*]Main Araniel as a Dunmer-Imperial Hybrid (white haired)
[*]Araniel as a Dunmer-Imperial Hybrid (black haired)
[/list][list]
[*]Original black haired Imperial-only style
[*]White haired, ashed skinned (ie mostly imperial)
[/list]
See the images for examples of their whole appearance.

[size=3]Installation:[/size]

[size=3]Requirements:[/size]
Designed with a UUNP-type body in mind
